      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n練習は順調に進んでますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work.\nPractice is going well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5661678791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ。ただ、ちょっとだけ心配事があって……\nあくまでちょっとしたことなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… But‚ there’s just one small thing I’m worried about…\nIt’s just a small thing though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9328342278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "些細であっても心配事は心配事だろ？\nなんでも相談してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it’s trivial‚ a worry is a worry‚ right?\nFeel free to talk to me about anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1333330552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、ありがとうございます\n最近……琴乃ちゃんが変なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ thank you.\nRecently… Kotono-chan has been acting strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2376861095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え、琴乃が変？\nつ、疲れてるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ Kotono’s been acting strange?\nI-Is she tired?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7333335639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、ある程度の疲れはあると思います\nでも近頃はぐっすり眠れてるみたいですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I think she’s probably tired to some extent.\nBut she seems to be getting a good night’s sleep lately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5777105809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、学校や仕事が終わると「用事があるから」\nってそそくさと私を置いて帰っちゃうんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ when school or work ends‚ she says‚ “I have something to do‚”\nand quickly leaves me behind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2110439142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "こんなこと今までなかったんです\nどうしたのかなって心配で心配で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This has never happened before.\nI’m so worried about what happened…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4811460496,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}